  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the garlic powder, garam masala, cumin powder, and salt, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the tomato puree and water, and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and add the chickpeas to the pan.",
    "Simmer the mixture for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve over rice or with naan bread."
